 for the dog's health above all.",[12,1524,1526],{"id":1525},"about-the-bunnies","About the Bunnies",[1528,1529,1530,1539,1547,1555],"ul",{},[1531,1532,1533],"li",{},[261,1534,1538],{"href":1535,"rel":1536},"https:\u002F\u002Ftailwindcss.tw",[1537],"nofollow","Tailwind CSS Taiwan Official Site",[1531,1540,1541,1546],{},[261,1542,1545],{"href":1543,"rel":1544},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Ftailwindcss.tw",[1537],"Tailwind CSS Taiwan"," (Facebook page)",[1531,1548,1549,1554],{},[261,1550,1553],{"href":1551,"rel":1552},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Fgroups\u002Ftailwindcss.taiwan",[1537],"Bunny Sect × Tailwind CSS Taiwan"," (Facebook community)",[1531,1556,1557],{},[261,1558,1561],{"href":1559,"rel":1560},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.facebook.com\u002Flalarabbits-%E5%85%94%E5%85%94%E6%95%99%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%AC%E7%87%9F-102150975410839\u002F",[1537],"Bunny Sect HQ",[17,1563,1564],{},[395,1565],{"alt":1566,"src":1567},"Bunny power knows no bounds","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FPwE2UE9.jpg",[1569,1570,1571],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sj_SG, html code.shiki .sj_SG{--shiki-default:#DBB7FF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}",{"title":38,"searchDepth":52,"depth":52,"links":1573},[1574,1575,1576,1577,1578,1579,1580,1581],{"id":14,"depth":52,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":52,"text":23},{"id":407,"depth":52,"text":408},{"id":832,"depth":52,"text":833},{"id":992,"depth":52,"text":992},{"id":1176,"depth":52,"text":1176},{"id":1518,"depth":52,"text":1519},{"id":1525,"depth":52,"text":1526},"Python","2021-09-16 00:00:10","Let's talk about modules in Python. JavaScript has its own idea of modules too, so we'll compare the two side by side — how to split your code into a separate file, export it, and import it back. Plus a couple of handy built-ins, dir() and help(), that make exploring modules way easier.","md","en",{},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-15-modules","7",{"title":6,"description":1584},false,"en\u002FPython\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-15-modules",[1582,1594,1595,1596],"JavaScript","Learn Python From a JavaScript Angle","第 13 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F16\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-15-modules\u002F","cN2wh8aq-2-HFNPe-2pwyBShal9cfsIbjrdAtmSNGU0",{"newer":1601,"older":1605},{"url":1602,"title":1603,"date":1604},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F17\u002Fpython-16-pip\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (16) - pip","2021-09-17 00:00:10",{"url":1606,"title":1607,"date":1608},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F15\u002Flearning-python-from-javascript-14-bmi-calculator-2\u002F","Learning Python From a JavaScript Angle (14) - Building a BMI Calculator, Part 2","2021-09-15 00:00:10",[1610,1615,1620],{"url":1611,"title":1612,"date":1613,"readingMinutes":1614},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F10\u002F02\u002Flearn-python-from-javascript-31-finale\u002F","Learning Python from a JavaScript Angle (31): So What Do You Want to Learn Next?","2021-10-02 00:00:05","4",{"url":1616,"title":16